com.okta.scim.util.model

Class SCIMResourceQueryResponse

  • Object
    • com.okta.scim.util.model.SCIMResourceQueryResponse
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    SCIMGroupQueryResponse, SCIMUserQueryResponse

    public class SCIMResourceQueryResponse
extends Object
    This class represents a response to a Query (GET) on the SCIM Server. SCIM Server should support pagination in the way specified in this class. Every page in the response should have the totalResults, startIndex and the itemsPerPage.
